OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,FThe health watchdog has raised safety
OL,7,Fconcerns over urgent and emergency
OL,8,Fcare at Bath's Royal United Hospital,
OL,9,Fafter inspectors found staff were
OL,10,Fworking under "enormous" pressure in
OL,11,Fan "overcrowded" environment.
OL,13,FIt comes after the Care Quality
OL,14,FCommission was alerted to safety
OL,15,Fconcerns about the emergency
OL,16,Fdepartment at Combe Park.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,FThey subsequently found it "didn't
OL,7,Fhave enough senior doctors overnight"
OL,8,Fand people with mental health needs
OL,9,Ftypically waited seven hours for a
OL,10,Fbed, in a loud environment.
OL,12,FFollowing the inspection last October,
OL,13,Fthe watchdog has downgraded the
OL,14,F"caring" rating of urgent and
OL,15,Femergency care from "good" to
OL,16,F"requires improvement".
OL,18,FIt said the department could also be
OL,19,Fsafer, more responsive and better-led.
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@eO]wD@UOUwD@ZO]xD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,FThe overall rating for Bath's Royal
OL,7,FUnited Hospital remains as "requires
OL,8,Fimprovement" and the rating for the
OL,9,FNHS Foundation Trust remains as "good".
OL,11,FCatherine Campbell, CQC deputy
OL,12,Fdirector of hospitals for secondary
OL,13,Fand specialist care in the South West,
OL,14,Fsaid: "When we inspected urgent and
OL,15,Femergency care at Royal United
OL,16,FHospital Bath, we found a department
OL,17,Funder enormous and unsustainable
OL,18,Fpressure, but staff were still working
OL,19,Fas hard as they could under the
OL,20,Fcircumstances, to try and provide safe
OL,21,Fcare and treatment to people.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@LO]qD@aOUqD@fO]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,F"The most pressing concerns were
OL,7,Faround safety. The department didn't
OL,8,Fhave enough senior doctors overnight,
OL,9,Ffalling below national guidelines, and
OL,10,Fnursing vacancy and sickness rates
OL,11,Fwere high.
OL,13,F"This left gaps in cover that leaders
OL,14,Fstruggled to fill, and when agency or
OL,15,Fbank staff were brought in, they
OL,16,Fdidn't always have the specialist
OL,17,Fskills needed to manage complex
OL,18,Femergencies which could put people at
OL,19,Frisk.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,F"Overcrowding created real physical
OL,7,Frisks to people. During our
OL,8,Finspection, trolleys were blocking the
OL,9,Fentrance to the children's
OL,10,Fresuscitation room and fire escape
OL,11,Froutes, meaning that in an emergency,
OL,12,Fthe team's response could have been
OL,13,Fdelayed.
OL,15,F"We were pleased that leaders acted
OL,16,Fquickly to address this when we raised
OL,17,Fit to them to help prevent people
OL,18,Fcoming to harm.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,F"People with mental health needs were
OL,7,Falso particularly affected. Some
OL,8,Fwaited an average of seven hours for a
OL,9,Fbed in a loud and busy environment
OL,10,Fwhich they found difficult to cope
OL,11,Fwith. This is longer than anyone
OL,12,Fshould have to wait in those
OL,13,Fcircumstances.
OL,15,F"We've shared our findings with the
OL,16,Ftrust, so they know where improvements
OL,17,Fmust be made and where there is good
OL,18,Fcare to build on.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,F"Leaders have assured us they're
OL,7,Ftaking our concerns seriously and
OL,8,Ftaking steps to improve the care and
OL,9,Fsupport people receive. We'll continue
OL,10,Fto monitor this service to ensure
OL,11,Fpeople are kept safe."
OL,13,FIn response to the watchdog's
OL,14,Ffindings, a spokesperson for the RUH
OL,15,Fsaid they had improved staffing and
OL,16,Foversight of emergency access points.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,FThey added: "We are working with the
OL,7,FAvon and Wiltshire Partnership so that
OL,8,Fpatients who are attending ED with
OL,9,Fmental health presentations are cared
OL,10,Ffor in the right place, at the right
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"The report also highlights positive
OL,14,Faspects of our service including our
OL,15,Fperformance against unplanned
OL,16,Freattendances and the appropriate
OL,17,Fescalation of suspected sepsis, high
OL,18,FNEWS2 scores and safeguarding concerns.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,F"Our staff are also recognised for
OL,7,Fbeing caring and compassionate,
OL,8,Fparticularly in how they look after
OL,9,Fthose patients with autism and
OL,10,Flearning disabilities.
OL,12,F"At the time of the visit and since
OL,13,Fthen, we have been experiencing the
OL,14,Fhighest ever demand levels in our
OL,15,FEmergency Department.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,F"In addition, the implementation of
OL,7,Fthe ambulance service's new Rapid
OL,8,FRelease Protocol coincided with a year-
OL,9,Fon-year ambulance demand increase of
OL,10,F25% and Emergency Department footfall
OL,11,Fof 13%.
OL,13,F"We have been working hard to respond
OL,14,Fto these new working practices
OL,15,Falongside South West Ambulance Service
OL,16,FFoundation Trust to make sure that it
OL,17,Fdoes not result in overcrowding in the
OL,18,FDepartment and we are committed to
OL,19,Fputting the right measures in place to
OL,20,Favoid corridor care in the hospital
OL,21,Fduring the course of next Winter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778764274
OL,3,CHealth watchdog raises safety concerns
OL,4,Cover care at emergency department
OL,6,F"We know from the end-of-year data
OL,7,Fthat we will be one of the most
OL,8,Fimproved Trusts in the country against
OL,9,Fthe 4-hour Emergency Department
OL,10,Ftarget; and we are pleased to have
OL,11,Fsecured access to capital funding to
OL,12,Fbuild a new Urgent Treatment Centre
OL,13,Fthis year and to completely rebuild
OL,14,Fthe Emergency Department over the
OL,15,Fcourse of the following three years."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
